---
title: Mexican Lentil Enchiladas with Tomato Salsa & Plant-Based Sour Cream
description: With wholesome lentils, mini flour tortillas, Cheddar cheese and salsa, this Mexican favourite is colourful,
delicious and a heap of fun. Don’t forget to dollop on the plant-based sour cream to really get the fiesta going!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/mexican-lentil-enchiladas-a56afd4a.jpg
